headline: Expedia (EXPE) Target Reduced by Citigroup Following Latest Results
summary: Expedia Group, Inc. (NASDAQ:EXPE) is included among the 13 Most Promising Long-Term Stocks to Buy According to Hedge Funds. On February 23, Citigroup lowered its price recommendation on Expedia Group, Inc. (NASDAQ:EXPE) to $225 from $281. It reiterated a Neutral rating on the shares. headline: 1 Internet Stock to Target This Week and 2 We Turn Down
summary: Whether it be online shopping or social media, secular forces are propelling consumer internet businesses forward. Despite the tailwinds, their demand largely hinges on consumer spending habits, which investors believe are weakening. As a result, the industry has pulled back by 27.8% over the past six months. This drawdown is a far cry from the S&P 500’s 6.2% ascent.
